🎮 GAME OVERVIEW
════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

STACK HEIST is a touch-optimized mobile stacking game where players drop blocks
to build a tower. Every 10 blocks triggers a HEIST EVENT where you must remove
a block without collapsing the tower!

Core Loop:
→ Block slides left/right at top
→ Tap to drop onto tower
→ Perfect alignment = multiplier growth
→ Wobbles cause instability
→ Heist every 10 blocks = risk/reward decision

