🎯 GAME TIPS
════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

FOR BEGINNERS:
→ Aim for perfect drops early to build multiplier
→ Don't risk bottom blocks in early heists
→ Save skip tokens for towers over 40 blocks
→ Golden blocks are worth keeping

ADVANCED:
→ 5 perfects in a row = +2 multiplier bonus
→ Bottom block removal = huge risk but massive reward
→ Watch tower wobble count (3 = warning, 5 = collapse)
→ Ghost blocks create uncertainty - check during heists
→ Bomb blocks can be used strategically to remove bad sections

HEIST STRATEGY:
• Safe: Remove top 1/3 of tower (85-95% success)
• Medium: Remove middle (60-75% success)
• Risky: Remove bottom (30-50% success, 2x bonus)
• Power block removal = guaranteed 2x bonus

